id.description: Div id with which to render the SDPlot

data.description: Data to render in the plot

className.description: class to give to SDPlot div

traceTypes.description: Types of each of the traces in the plot

traceNames.description: Names for each of the traces

barmode.description: Type of bar chart to plot

bargap.description: Gap between the bars in barplot

palette.description: Array of colors to use for the traces

xName.description: Name of the x data series

xLabel.description: Label for the x data series to display

xTickLabels.description: Array of tick labels to use

xTicksPrefix.description: Prefix to use for x ticks

xTicksFormat.description: d3 formatting string to format x ticks

xType.description: d3 formatting string to format x values

xRangemode.description: Type of range to use for the x axis

yNames.description: Names of the y data series

yLabel.description: Label for the y data series to display

yTicksPrefix.description: Prefix to use for y ticks

yTicksFormat.description: d3 formatting string to format y ticks

yHoverFormat.description: d3 formatting string to format y values on hover

yType.description: d3 formatting string to format y values

yRangemode.description: Type of range to use for the y axis

horizontalLines.description: Display horizontal lines on the chart?

verticalLines.description: Display vertical lines on the chart?

gridColor.description: Color to make horizontal/vertical lines on the chart

showLegend.description: Display the legend for the chart?

legendLocation.description: Location of the chart legend, if displayed

legendBackgroundColor.description: Background color for the chart legend, if displayed

legendBorderColor.description: Border color for the chart legend, if displayed

fontFamily.description: Name of the font family to use for text

fontScale.description: Scaling factor for the font, relative to 1

fontColor.description: Color to use for the font

resizeDebounce.description: ms gap during which only the latest window resize event should cause a redraw

redrawDebounce.description: ms gap during which only the latest redraw requested should occur
